  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the safety and efficacy of interferon beta (Betaseron) in AIDS and advanced AIDS
      related complex (ARC) patients receiving a reduced-dose zidovudine (AZT) regimen.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
